Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,5,,泪的咆哮 你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是…鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种压迫感是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那红色的查克拉又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不把你送给大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把你的手脚给折断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该清醒点了吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是还没清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你打到动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这既没父母也没兄弟的混小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能体会我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小就孤单一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底能明白些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有着亲情的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了他们之后的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又怎么能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不了解真正的父母兄弟之情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我请客 你就放开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和伊鲁卡老师在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾想象过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做忍者还是得先填饱肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乘机大吃一顿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否就是这样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你在一起的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 你这拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想兄弟或许就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会如此对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好不容易得来的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…一定要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会再回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来斩断这份羁绊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要斩断这份羁绊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么到现在还戴着护额
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认 你是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你和我一样都了解孤独的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这份痛苦 会让人变得坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此 我才要斩断这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而得到更为强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 我要和你平等对决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法伤到我额头的一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点是永远不会改变的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来和你说什么都是白费口舌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲聊就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 你我之间只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才一直无法捕捉的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可以看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的动作和之前完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 决不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为身体渐渐习惯了咒印状态的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙移动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身微妙的力道分布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他的下一个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚地浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有此眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会白白浪费查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为咒印实在太消耗体力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然能看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只要掌握先机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对准此刻看到的鸣人之后的动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的动作完全被他看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这条路没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.龙火之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 你真够弱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大爷我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再感谢一下把我封印在\N你这种小鬼体内的第四代火影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经看穿了鸣人的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他身上的查克拉却做出了不同的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去查克拉好像有意识自己在动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我的眼睛也无法看透
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股红色的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非寻常的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标果然是鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带走鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的组织晓所下达的至上命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你小子有着特别的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我总算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那种查克拉保护着他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持距离作战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就抓不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能躲开就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦借用了这股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后会变成什么样我也不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也没办法啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你更特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 身体好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 左手几乎毫无感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这股力量并不能一直用下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的一击 就是最后的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪雨的终结
